		{
			"type": "action",
			"name": "Draining Slam",
			"system": {
				"actionType": {
					"value": "passive"
				},
				"description": {
					"value": "<p>When a creature is hit by the blightforged's slam Strike, that creature must attempt at a @Check[fortitude|dc:19] save. Regardless of the result, the target is then immune for 1 minute.</p><hr /><p><strong>Critical Success</strong> the creature is unaffected.</p><p><strong>Success</strong> the creature is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.MIRkyAjyBeXivMa7]{Enfeebled 1}.</p><p><strong>Failure</strong> the creature is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.MIRkyAjyBeXivMa7]{Enfeebled 2} and @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.4D2KBtexWXa6oUMR]{Drained 1}.</p><p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> the creature is enfeebled 2 and @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.4D2KBtexWXa6oUMR]{Drained 2}.</p>",
